Class CustomerReview

java.lang.Object
CustomerReview
public class CustomerReview extends Object
Represents a customer review with a customer name and their latest review Two CustomerReview objects are considered equal if they have the same customer name
Version:
2.17.2026
Author:
Ali Kablanbek
